    <data key="d0">Anchor Operating System: Building a Serverless Guest Sightseeing Journey Seamlessly</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c-1GXhOOOww</data>
    <data key="d2">Serverless ticketing system serving 40+ tenants. Employs multi-tenancy in DynamoDB using partition keys, and isolates static assets on S3 and APIs via AppSync and API Gateway.</data>
